review_text: Baru pertama kali berlibur ke kota Bsnyuwangi dan dua kali sudah mengunjungi restoran ini. Akan menjadi resto favorit bila berkunjung lagi ke Banyuwangi. Semuanya sangat baik, dari mulai staff nya yang ramah - ramah, terutama dg pak rivan (kalau saya tidak salah ingat), beliau mendeskripsikan jenis makanan yg masih asing di telinga, dengan penjelasan yang sangat baik dan ramah, makanannya pun semua mantap rasanya (yang kami coba diantaranya rujak soto, ayam geprek sayur koro, ayam lodoh, ayam betutu, ayam goreng plecing kangkung, penyet tempe), ada juga aneka jajanan pasar yang menurut saya juga mantap rasanya (jenang/aneka bubur, pastel, kue cucur, klepon), semua benar2 memanjakan lidah, mantap ! Untuk minumannya pun banyak jenisnya, berbagai minuman tradisional yang menurut saya enak dan tidak asing di lidah (yg perbah dicoba bir pletok, jakutes, dan seruni). Suasana restorannya yang tenang, berkesan tradisional dan bersih, bahkan sampai ke area cuci tangan dan toilet pun resik, suka dengan suasana restorannya. Dan yang paling penting adalah harga menu makanan dan minumannya masih terjangkau, berkisar antara 15 rb - 40 rb. Mantap lah ! Tetap pertahankan ya seperti ini, very recommended !
review_translated_text: This is my first vacation to Bsnyuwangi city and I have visited this restaurant twice. Will be a favorite restaurant when you visit Banyuwangi again. Everything was very good, starting from the friendly staff, especially Mr. Rivan (if I remember correctly), he described types of food that were still foreign to the ear, with very good and friendly explanations, the food all tasted great (which we tried, including rujak soto, fried chicken vegetable koro, chicken lodoh, chicken betutu, fried chicken plecing kangkung, penyet tempe), there are also various market snacks which I think also taste delicious (jenang/various porridge, pastels, cucur cakes, klepon) , everything really pampers the tongue, great! There are many types of drinks, various traditional drinks which I think are delicious and familiar to the palate (Ive tried bir pletok, jakutes and seruni). The atmosphere of the restaurant is calm, traditional and clean, even the hand washing area and toilets are clean, I like the atmosphere of the restaurant. And the most important thing is that the prices for the food and drink menu are still affordable, ranging from 15 thousand - 40 thousand. Thats great! Keep it up like this, highly recommended!

review_translated_text: Order 2 jumbo portions for a small family, crab and lobster. Size according to price. The sauce is very delicious, I like it.... The children looked happy eating crab and lobster shells, because it was like a handicraft, heheheeeee The location is strategic on the side of the main road. However, it can be dangerous if you leave the restaurant heading south, because it is located right on the corner. So every time I come home from this restaurant, I have to go north via the bridge thats close by. Oh yes, at night it was stiflingly hot, even though the hanging fan right above was spinning but wasnt strong enough to blow the wind. I observed that the hanging fan blades were almost flat, they needed to be bent so that the wind could blow fast. BTW, for me, the only place in the city of Kediri that serves seafood dishes like this with delicious sauce...

Flavor Chicken sweet & sour Rawon fried rice Capcay Ocean blue Iced tea Spaghetti Ice cream All the menus I ordered were in the delicious category I dont know why this chef cooks so well, is it true that the menu I ordered is all delicious? Thank you chef & all crew Place Comfortable, cool & clean AC men and womens toilets are different The parking lot is not spacious enough for a car baby chair can cash & debit Price Affordable compared to the taste & really comfortable place, a homiii cafe With a varied menu, this is a cool cafe, you know... Sudah lama nggak ke bledeg, terakhir mungkin tahun 2020 waktu itu fish n chip isinya masih gede-gede dan siomay nya juga beneran siomay (gede, isi ikan bukan siomay frozen food kecil-kecil). Nah sekarang libur lebaran 2023 nyobain kesini lagi karena istri ngidam pengen ke bledeg. Ya intinya turunkan ekspektasimu, kalau mau kesini lagi dan berharap bledeg masih sama seperti dulu kamu akan kecewa. Meskipun begitu bledeg ini termasuk hebat masih mampu bertahan buka sampai sekarang disaat kafe dan resto lain yang seangkatan satu persatu kolaps dan gulung tikar. Ya semoga bledeg bisa berjaya lagi seperti dulu tahun 2016-2020, banyak kenangan saya dan istri disini soalnya.
response_from_owner_text: makasi kaka untuk reviewnya, ditunggu kedatangannya lagi :)
review_translated_text: Its been a long time since Ive been to bledeg, the last time was maybe 2020, when the fish n chip filling was still big and the siomay were really siomay (big, filled with fish, not small frozen food siomay). So, now for the 2023 Eid holidays, try coming here again because my wife wants to go to Bledeg. Yes, the point is to lower your expectations, if you want to come here again and expect the bledeg to still be the same as before you will be disappointed. Even so, this bledeg is considered great, still able to stay open until now when other cafes and restaurants of the same generation are collapsing and going out of business one by one. Yes, I hope Bledeg can be successful again like before in 2016-2020, there are lots of memories for me and my wife here.
response_from_owner_translated_text: Thank you bro for the review, we look forward to seeing you again :)

review_text: Pertama kali dine in di resto ini karena biasanya nitip teman kerja buat dimakan di kantor  . Tempatnya agak masuk, tapi masih gampang dijangkau kendaraan roda 2 maupun 4, kalau naik kendaraan umum perlu jalan kaki sekitar 700 meteran. Kemaren kita parkir mobil pas di depan resto dan sedikit makan jalan, tapi sepertinya di dalam bisa juga buat parkir kendaraan. Open resto, jadi ndak pakai AC ya, tapi karena kita kesana pas malam ndak terasa terlalu panas. Harga yang ditawarkan affordable, makanannya juga enak, mungkin karena itu tempat ini ramai. Cuman kalo lagi terlalu rame jadi kurang nyaman juga karena jarak antar meja lumayan mepet. Sayangnya, karena open, banyak juga yang merokok di dalam, jadi kurang recomended buat yang bawa anak kecil untuk makan di dalam restonya, mungkin perlu dibedakan tempat yang boleh merokok sama ndak boleh merokok. Penyajian makanannya juga cepat, cocok deh buat yang udah kelaperan. Suami suka sama beras kencurnya. Metode pembayaran gampang menerima cash dan cashless. And the most important staffnya ramah, suka banget.
review_translated_text: First time eating at this restaurant because I usually entrust my work friends to eat at the office  . The place is a bit in, but still easy to reach by 2 or 4 wheeled vehicles, if you take public transportation you need to walk about 700 meters. Yesterday we parked the car right in front of the restaurant and walked a bit, but it looks like you can also park your vehicle inside. The restaurant is open, so it doesnt use AC, but because we went there at night it didnt feel too hot. The prices offered are affordable, the food is also delicious, maybe thats why this place is busy. But if its too busy, it wont be comfortable because the distance between the tables is quite tight. Unfortunately, because its open, there are lots of people smoking inside, so its not recommended for those bringing small children to eat in the restaurant, maybe you need to differentiate between places where you can smoke and where you cant. However the place is nice, clean and photoable. There are many food and drink menus, and so far my favorite menu is tuna. For chicken with salted egg sauce, I personally think its actually delicious, but the portion of salted egg sauce is not enough, and the flour is a bit hard for kids. The food served is also fast, suitable for those who are already hungry. My husband likes his kencur rice. Payment methods are easy to accept cash and cashless. And the most important thing is that the staff is friendly, they really like it.

review_translated_text: In my opinion, this place is recommended as a place to shop for souvenirs, a bakery and also to eat heavy meals. The parking area is also spacious. On the 1st floor at the front is a place where bakery products are sold. Going deeper is the place for various souvenirs (various crafts, t-shirts), there is also a place for various types of coffee products. Going deeper is a paradise for souvenirs from typical Blambangan earth food products. If you want to eat heavy food, you can do it in the open space area (patio) and inside (2nd floor). Diverse menu. Prices also vary. Note: If you go to this place, keep your faith and dont be hungry. Because thats where your wallet starts to break. Btw, please visit.

review_text: Rencana mau makan malam di jam 19:00 tanggal 13 April. Sudah duduk, lihat menu, ketika taking order waiter sudah bilang memang ada beberapa menu yg tidak tersedia. Krn itu jelas kita pesan menu yg dia bilang tersedia. Bbrp saat kemudian, sepertinya manager resto bersama waiter yg taking order pesanan kami datang ke meja memberi tahu bahwa hanya 1 menu yg available yaitu mangut pari. Saran saya kenapa dari awal pertama kali tamu datang ketika di-greet langsung saja beri tahu bahwa yg tersedia MISALKAN hanya ada snacks dan kopi. Seperti tidak ada komunikasi antara kitchen department dan server. Atau bisa beli papan ditempatkan di area pintu masuk ditulis apa saja yg sudah soldout/hanya tersedia apa saja. Padahal ambience restonya enak sekali loh, cuman sayang jd pengalaman buruk dengan servicenya. Semoga kedepannya servicenya bisa diperbaiki.
response_from_owner_text: Dear Ibu Azalia, Minal aidin wal faizin, Selamat Hari Raya Idul Fitri 1445 H. Kami sangat senang dan berterimakasih ibu telah berkunjung ke Omah Majapahit Cafe & Resto Banyuwangi. Tetapi di saat yang sama kami juga menyesal tidak-dapat memberikan pelayanan yang baik kepada Ibu dan keluarga. Kami memohon maaf atas ketidak-nyamanan ini, feedback atau masukan ini akan segera kami tindak-lanjuti. Mohon dapat berkunjung kembali dalam waktu dekat dan berkenan untuk menginformasikan melalui layanan reservasi / staff kami di nomor WA 0819-7700-7117. Sekali lagi besar harapan kami untuk kita dapat bertemu kembali. Salam Rahayu. Management Omah Majapahit Cafe & Resto
review_translated_text: Plan to have dinner at 19:00 on April 13th. Already sat down, looked at the menu, when taking the order the waiter said that there were several menus that were not available. Because of that, we obviously ordered the menu that he said was available. A few moments later, it seemed like the restaurant manager and the waiter who took our order came to the table to tell us that only 1 menu was available, namely mangut pari. My advice is why from the first time guests arrive when they are greeted, just tell them straight away that what is available FOR EXAMPLE is only snacks and coffee. Like there is no communication between the kitchen department and the server. Or you can buy a board placed in the entrance area to write down what is sold out/what is only available. Even though the ambience of the restaurant is really nice, its just a shame that the experience was bad with the service. Hopefully in the future the service can be improved.
response_from_owner_translated_text: Dear Mrs. Azalia, Minal aidin wal faizin, Happy Eid Al-Fitr 1445 H. We are very happy and grateful for visiting Omah Majapahit Cafe & Resto Banyuwangi. But at the same time we also regret not being able to provide good service to you and your family. We apologize for this inconvenience, we will immediately follow up on this feedback or input. Please visit again in the near future and be willing to inform us via our reservation service / staff on WA number 0819-7700-7117. Once again we have great hope that we can meet again. Greetings Rahayu. Management of Omah Majapahit Cafe & Resto

review_text: Ini sebetulnya tempat makan bagus sekali. Tidak ada yang bisa di katakan jelek bahkan kurang untuk suasana, vibes nya, interior, dan dekorasi hiasannya. Semua bagus sekali. Cocok untuk keluarga, bawa tamu, dan acara meeting / gathering. Ada musik latar yang pas dengan suasana, tidak kencang, juga tidak pelan. Untuk rasa dan harga, relatif. Tergantung lidah dan dompet masing masing. Jadi tidak bisa di bilang enak ataupun tidak enak. Silahkan coba sendiri. Satu hal yang saya perhatikan sedari datang, waiter nya. Mas yang satu ini betul betul paham hospitality. Pengunjung disambut dengan ramah dan senyum. Di kala pegawai yang lain nongkrong di meja kosong dan utak atik dengan HP nya, hanya dia yang selalu stand by di pos nya dengan memperhatikan sekeliling sekiranya ada tamu atau pelanggan yg butuh bantuan. Saat pulang pun kita di service ala hotel dengan greeting-nya. Begitupun dengan kang parkir nya, cuek bebek dengan saya. Mungkin karena bawa motor dan kaos oblong kali ya... hehe...

Rahayu, Management Omah Majapahit
review_translated_text: This is actually a really nice place to eat. There is nothing that can be said to be bad, even less so for the atmosphere, vibes, interior and decorative decorations. All very good. Suitable for families, bringing guests, and meeting / gathering events. There is background music that fits the atmosphere, not loud, not slow. For taste and price, relatively. Depends on each individuals tongue and wallet. So it cant be said to be good or bad. Please try it yourself. One thing I noticed when I arrived was the waiter. This bro really understands hospitality. Visitors are greeted with kindness and a smile. When other employees hang out at empty tables and fiddle with their cellphones, he is the only one who always stands by at his post, paying attention to his surroundings in case there are guests or customers who need help. When we returned home, we were given hotel-style service with greetings. Likewise with the parking lot, he ignored me. Maybe because you brought a motorbike and a T-shirt... hehe...
response_from_owner_translated_text: Dear Mr Aldo, Thank you for visiting and for your willingness to give us a good rating. We really hope that Mr. Aldo can help us in providing another review. Once again, thank you, best wishes and success always to Mr. Aldo and his family. Rahayu, Management Omah Majapahit

review_text: Tempat yang sangat saya rekomendasikan bagi anda yang ingin makan bersama keluarga, diskusi santai, kerja fokus dengan suasana yang nyaman, keren, asri dan percampuran modern dan vintage. Terdapat sajian roti dan kopi disini. Untuk harga memang cukup tinggi tapi terbayarkan dengan rasa dan suasana yang bagus disini. Tempat sedikit masuk jalan kecil tapi anda akan dibuat terkejut dengan isi dan suasana di dalamnya.
review_translated_text: A place that I highly recommend for those of you who want to eat with family, have relaxed discussions, focus on work in a comfortable, cool, beautiful atmosphere and a mix of modern and vintage. There is bread and coffee served here. The price is quite high but it pays off with the good taste and atmosphere here. The place is a little off a small road but you will be surprised by the contents and atmosphere inside.

review_text: Cafe dengan suasana yang elit dan tenang, cocok untuk bersantai, diskusi kerja, dan berkumpul. Makanan lebih banyak ke kue, roti dan beberapa makanan berat. Minuman tersedia dari jenis kopi, soda, dan milkshake. Untuk rate harga kurang lebih Rp, 20.000 keatas, tapi sepadan dengan suasana yang nyaman. Santai untuk siang/sore oke, kalau malam lebih estetik lagi karena ada lampu taman nya. Disediakan juga permainan yang menarik untuk menunggu makanan, atau sekedar menghabiskan waktu disana. Seperti uno, catur, bingo, dll. Staff ramah, tempat bersih estetik dan menarik, hiden gems yang mantapp Yang saya pesan: 1. Choco Biscoff roll Rp, 20.000 2. Ijenliebe caramel latte Rp, 31.000 Sukses, mantapp!
review_translated_text: Cafe with an elite and calm atmosphere, suitable for relaxing, work discussions and gatherings. Food is more like cakes, bread and some heavy foods. Drinks are available in the form of coffee, soda and milkshakes. The price rate is around IDR 20,000 and above, but its worth it for the comfortable atmosphere. Relaxing for the day/evening, okay, at night its even more aesthetic because there are garden lights. Interesting games are also provided for waiting for food, or just spending time there. Such as uno, chess, bingo, etc. Friendly staff, clean, aesthetic and attractive place, great hidden gems What I ordered: 1. Choco Biscoff roll Rp. 20,000 2. Ijenliebe caramel latte Rp. 31,000 Success, great!

review_text: Cafe dPoto hadir menambah khazanah kuliner di Situbondo. Tersedia ruangan indoor berpendingin udara maupun semi-outdoor. Tempatnya cukup nyaman dan dekat dengan pusat kota. Tempat parkirnya cukup luas. Harga masih terjangkau dan relatif sama dengan cafe-cafe sejenis di Situbondo. Saya dan keluarga suka dengan Ice Cream Cone-nya. Sementara hanya tersedia rasa vanila, cokelat, atau kombinasi keduanya. Semoga kedepannya lebih bervariasi, dan ada pilihan untuk es krimnya ditaruh di cup/mangkok kecil dan diberi sendok. Lebih mudah untuk pengunjung yang membawa anak kecil. Untuk makanan, menurut saya cukup enak. Hanya saja, untuk cafe sebesar dengan karyawati sebanyak itu, menurut saya menu makanannya kurang bervariasi. Hanya ada 12 menu nasi/mie dan 10 menu snack. Untuk minuman tersedia lebih banyak pilihan, mulai dari soda squash, milkshake, hingga aneka sajian kopi.
review_translated_text: Cafe dPoto is here to add to the culinary treasures of Situbondo. Air-conditioned indoor and semi-outdoor rooms are available. The place is quite comfortable and close to the city center. The parking lot is quite spacious. Prices are still affordable and relatively the same as similar cafes in Situbondo. My family and I like the Ice Cream Cone. While only available in vanilla, chocolate or a combination of both. Hopefully in the future there will be more variety, and there will be an option for the ice cream to be placed in a small cup/bowl and given a spoon. It is easier for visitors who bring small children. As for the food, I think its quite delicious. Its just that, for a cafe that big and with that many employees, in my opinion the food menu isnt varied enough. There are only 12 rice/noodle menus and 10 snack menus. For drinks, there are more choices available, from squash soda, milkshakes, to various coffee offerings.

Tidak tersedia Toilet,kalo udah kebelet bisa ke Toilet Mushola deket situ (tapi tidak dianjurkan sama sekali, karena walau dibilang Mushola Kamar Mandinya beuuuuhhhhhh  ) Over all,, semua OK..
review_translated_text: Modern cafe with a view of yachts in front.. Except for fried rice, all the food I ordered was delicious, which is cheaper (crying   ) The fried rice (whether it happened to be served to me by chance, or thats how it usually is) had a slightly dry texture, and the seasoning was almost non-existent. The fish and chips are a winner, the fish is crispy on the outside, soft on the inside, the cream is delicious, its delicious. The iced chocolate that I ordered tasted more like milk chocolate, not dark chocolate which is bitter. Payment here does not use E Money such as Ovo Pay, etc. Just use a debit machine (if Im not mistaken BNI debit machine). There are no toilets available, if you really need it, you can go to the prayer room toilet near there (but its not recommended at all, because even though it says its a prayer room, the bathroom is too big  ) Over all, everything is OK...

review_text: Coba chocolate ice cream tea break untuk pertama kali. Jujur out of my expectations, ice cream nya bukan seperti ice cream biasanya. Teksturnya lebih ke susu coklat yang dibekukan (tidak halus/creamy), atau mungkin memang dibuat seperti itu, atau cuma hari itu yg teksturnya tidak halus. Untuk rasanya kurang manis sedikit untuk saya. Sedikit saran, fat untuk bahan ice cream lebih banyak supaya tekstur lebih creamy, bisa juga harga sedikit dinaikkan tapi dengan kualitas yang tentu juga lebih baik. Terima kasih.
review_translated_text: Try chocolate ice cream tea break for the first time. Honestly, out of my expectations, the ice cream is not like normal ice cream. The texture is more like frozen chocolate milk (not smooth/creamy), or maybe it was made like that, or it was just that day that the texture wasnt smooth. It doesnt taste a little sweet for me. A little advice, there is more fat in the ice cream ingredients so that the texture is creamier, the price could also be increased a little but the quality is of course also better. Thank You.

review_text: Tea Break didirikan sejak tahun 2017 yang bertujuan untuk menyajikan minuman yang berkualitas dengan harga yang sangat terjangkau agar bisa dinikmati oleh semua kalangan masyarakat Indonesia. Kami selalu berinovasi untuk menciptakan varian terbaru yang sesuai dengan selera masyarakat Indonesia. about2 Untuk menjaga kualitas dan kepuasan pelanggan kami selalu berikan yang terbaik mulai dari bahan-bahan yang digunakan seperti teh, susu dan lain-lain, serta selalu menjaga pelayanan dan profesionalitas kami kepada semua pelanggan. Kini Tea Break terus berkembang pesat di seluruh kota Indonesia supaya semua kalangan masyarakat Indonesia bisa menikmati Tea Break.
review_translated_text: Tea Break was founded in 2017 with the aim of serving quality drinks at very affordable prices so that they can be enjoyed by all levels of Indonesian society. We always innovate to create the latest variants that suit the tastes of the Indonesian people. about2 To maintain quality and customer satisfaction, we always provide the best starting from the ingredients used such as tea, milk and others, and always maintain our service and professionalism to all customers. Now Tea Break continues to grow rapidly in all Indonesian cities so that all levels of Indonesian society can enjoy Tea Break.

review_text: Es teh yang viral & kekinian. Ditengah banyaknya serangan perkopian, Es Teh Indonesia berhasil menunjukan eksistensinya mengangkat derajat teh dengan berbagai varian rasa. Tempatnya di Jl. Veteran Gresik, satu tempat dengan kantor notaris. Pelayanannya ok, namun perlu ditingkatkan lagi kecepatan pelayanannya. Didalamnya terdapat beberapa kursi & meja untuk menunggu (atau mungkin minum ditempat), diluar hanya ada 1 baris kursi besi untuk menunggu. Tersedia parkir untuk motor, untuk mobil parkirnnya dibahu jalan, kalau malam harus berbagi parkir dengan parkiran penyetan disebelahnya. Pembayarannya bisa tunai & nontunai. Parking: Parkir terbatas untuk mobil.
review_translated_text: Viral & trendy iced tea. In the midst of many coffee attacks, Indonesian Es Teh has succeeded in showing its existence in raising the status of tea with various flavor variants. The place is on Jl. Veteran Gresik, the same place as the notarys office. The service is ok, but the speed of service needs to be improved. Inside there are several chairs & tables for waiting (or maybe drinking on the spot), outside there is only 1 row of metal chairs for waiting. Parking is available for motorbikes, parking for cars is on the side of the road, at night you have to share parking with the parking lot next to it. Payment can be cash & non-cash. Parking: Limited parking for cars.

review_text: Kuliner Warung Mak Tam in Kediri is a hidden gem for those seeking delicious and budget-friendly eats. With a vast menu that caters to all appetites, its a perfect spot for a casual hangout with family and friends. Whether youre craving a classic Indonesian bakso or something lighter like gelato, your wallet will thank you. Their gelato selection boasts incredibly affordable prices, starting at a mere 15,000 rupiah! Dont let the low cost fool you though   they also offer bakso premium for those who desire a more decadent version of this beloved Indonesian soup. The ambiance at Kuliner Warung Mak Tam is ideal for relaxation. Its a place where you can unwind and catch up with loved ones in a comfortable and casual setting. To complete your experience, be sure to try their signature flavorful milk   its a guaranteed crowd-pleaser and a true testament to their commitment to deliciousness at affordable prices. review_translated_text: Honestly, I am very disappointed with this place to eat. Not suitable to visit if you are very hungry and in a hurry. Because the service is very long. The first information when I paid at the cashier said it would take 15-20 minutes for the food to arrive. What I had to do was wait 45 minutes before the drink came. I was about to finish drinking, then after 65 minutes the food came. An hour of my time was wasted. When the restaurant waiter was asked, the answer was just wait a minute while looking away. There really is no etiquette at all. Its a shame even though the food is quite delicious. But for me, service must still come first. I was surprised that even though there were lots of waiters gathered around chatting happily in front of the kitchen door, why wasnt the food ready? Hope the service can be improved again. Because after all, service is a reflection of the quality of the place to eat.

Cuma untuk pembayaran cashless, akan dikenakan charge, baik itu debet ataupun qris. Saran aja: jika memang merchant terpotong dengan biaya qriss dll, includekan pada harga barang, jadi customer ga perlu dapat hitungan terpisah walaupun di akhir ada catatannya. Kedua saran toilet agak kurang besar, untungnya saya berbadan kecil, tapi saya membayangkan untuk orang tua atau bertubuh gemuk agak susah, karena posisi toilet agak naik dan ketika menutup pintu kesulitan. Parking: Parkir luas, mobil dan motor luas. Saat saya datang ga ada kang parkir sih. Kid-friendliness: Ada kursi anak bayi.
review_translated_text: There are lots of food choices, even the food menu is quite complete. The portions are also big, the bakwan is big. Spacious parking. Only for cashless payments, a charge will be charged, be it debit or qris. Just a suggestion: if the merchant deducts qriss fees, etc., include them in the price of the goods, so the customer doesnt need to get a separate calculation even though there is a note at the end. The second suggestion is that the toilet is a bit small, fortunately I have a small body, but I imagine it would be difficult for older or fat people, because the position of the toilet is a bit up and it is difficult to close the door. Parking: Spacious parking, spacious cars and motorbikes. When I arrived there was no parking. Kid-friendliness: There is an infant child seat.

#edit ulasan. Semakin kesini rasa makanannya biasa-biasa saja. Bahkan saya dan keluarga sempat kecewa dengan masakan yg kami pesan ada sebagian yg belum matang. Dan ketika saya coba datang lagi beberapa minggu kemudian dengan beberapa teman, masih juga mendapatkan makanan yg kami pesan ada yg belum matang, dan rasanya juga masih tetap sama, biasa saja. Tapi ada beberapa menu yg rasanya enak. Padahal dulu jadi tempat favorit utk nongkrong... Menu yg saya pesan waktu itu yg belum matang sempurna : 1. Nasi goreng. Nasinya belum matang. Jadi rasanya kayak makan beras digoreng  . 2. Tahu walik. Diluar matang, dalemnya masih rasa tepung. 3. Bebek goreng. Nasinya belum matang, bebeknya keras dan masih bau amis, juga saya rasakan belum matang. 4. Siomay. Isian siomaynya ada beberapa yg masih belum matang. 5. Mie goreng. Yg saya rasakan mie nya masih mentah dan rasa bumbunya hambar. Untuk menu yg lain masih oke lah. Dan pelayanannya ramah Sekedar saran. Mungkin sebelum disajikan ada baiknya dicek dulu. Padahal dulu hampir semua rasa masakannya endul banget.
response_from_owner_text: Terima kasih atas ulasannya... mohon di infokan menu apa yang belum matang agar menjadi perhatian dan perbaikan kami di kemudian hari... terima kasih
review_translated_text: #edit review. The food here tastes mediocre. In fact, my family and I were disappointed with the dishes we ordered, some of which were not yet cooked. And when I tried to come again a few weeks later with some friends, I still got the food we ordered that was not yet cooked, and the taste was still the same, just normal. But there are several menus that taste delicious. Even though it used to be a favorite place to hang out... The menu that I ordered at that time was not fully cooked: 1. Fried rice. The rice is not cooked yet. So it feels like eating fried rice  . 2. Know the guardian. When cooked outside, the inside still tastes of flour. 3. Fried duck. The rice wasnt cooked yet, the duck was hard and still smelled fishy, I also felt it wasnt cooked yet. 4. Siomay. Some of the dumpling fillings are still not cooked. 5. Fried noodles. What I tasted was that the noodles were still raw and the seasoning tasted bland. The other menus are still okay. And the service is friendly Just a suggestion. Maybe before serving it would be a good idea to check first. Even though in the past almost all the dishes tasted really delicious.
response_from_owner_translated_text: Thank you for your review... please let us know what menu items are not yet cooked so that we can pay attention and improve them in the future... thank you

review_text: We went to eat dinner around 7:45 p.m., when we placed our order they told us that the dish ordered was sold out. So we make another choice, it turns out that this one is also sold out. We therefore take the bakso bakar dish which is in fact a simple bowl of 9 dumplings (despite being delicious but very light for a meal...). We then decide to finish with a dessert: the chocolate fondant and the waiter responds once again and with a smile that it is also sold out... The least you can do is warn in advance and apologize when so many dishes are missing from a menu!
review_translated_text: Nous sommes alles manger le diner vers 19h45, au moment de passer commande ils nous annoncent que le plat commande est sold out. Nous faisons donc un autre choix, il savere que celui-ci est egalement sold out. Nous prenons donc le plat bakso bakar qui est en fait un simple bol de 9 boulettes (malgre tout delicieuses mais tres leger pour un repas...). On decide alors de terminer par un dessert : le fondant au chocolat et le serveur repond une nouvelle fois et avec le sourire que cest aussi sold out... La moindre des choses est de prevenir en avance et de sexcuser lorsquil manque autant de plats sur une carte !

A varied food menu of light and heavy foods is all available, such as egg toast snacks, mendoan, burgers, fried rice, noodles, fried rice with lung tripe. Kebuli rice, rice bowls, etc. Recommendations for snacks that are delicious to the eye, in my opinion, are tempeh mendoan, chili tofu, cireng and bucked snacks. Recommended drinks: Blushing heart, blue ocean paradise, lechy tea. The comfortable atmosphere is available in outdoor, indoor and lesehan places. Friendly service and employees ready to provide food and drink recommendations if you are visiting for the first time. Clean toilet facilities, Uno stick toys and pretty fast wifi. Ample parking for cars and motorbikes and paid parking, guys. Overall, the place is cozy and spacious, the food and drinks are okay at pocket-friendly prices. Fast service for dine in or take away. Parking: Strategic location right across the Mojoroto intersection, spacious parking for cars and motorbikes. Paid parking for motorbikes 2,000 and cars 4,000

review_text: Tamulang Co-Working Space and Cafe adalah kafe sekaligus ruang kerja bersama (co-working space) yang pertama di Banyuwangi. Kafe ini berlokasi di Jalan Badung, Kelurahan Tamanbaru, Banyuwangi, dan buka setiap hari dari pukul 11.00 hingga 23.00 WIB. Tamulang Co-Working Space and Cafe memiliki konsep yang asri dan nyaman, dengan banyak sulur tanaman rindang yang menghiasi ruangan. Kafe ini juga menyediakan berbagai fasilitas untuk menunjang aktivitas bekerja, seperti Wi-Fi gratis, stopkontak, dan ruang meeting. Selain sebagai tempat kerja, Tamulang Co-Working Space and Cafe juga merupakan tempat yang tepat untuk bersantai dan menikmati berbagai makanan dan minuman yang lezat. Menu yang ditawarkan di kafe ini cukup beragam, mulai dari makanan berat seperti nasi ayam lado hijau dan bakmie tamulang, hingga makanan ringan seperti tahu walik dan siomay. Untuk minuman, kafe ini menawarkan berbagai varian kopi, teh, dan jus.
review_translated_text: Tamulang Co-Working Space and Cafe is the first cafe and co-working space in Banyuwangi. This cafe is located on Jalan Badung, Tamanbaru Village, Banyuwangi, and is open every day from 11.00 to 23.00 WIB. Tamulang Co-Working Space and Cafe has a beautiful and comfortable concept, with lots of shady plants decorating the room. This cafe also provides various facilities to support work activities, such as free Wi-Fi, power outlets and meeting rooms. Apart from being a place to work, Tamulang Co-Working Space and Cafe is also a great place to relax and enjoy a variety of delicious food and drinks. The menu offered at this cafe is quite varied, ranging from heavy foods such as green chicken lado rice and guestlang noodles, to light foods such as tofu walik and dumplings. For drinks, this cafe offers various variants of coffee, tea and juice.

review_text: Kovii Cafe, Kediri: Tempat Santai dan Enak untuk Bersantap Kovii Cafe di Kediri adalah salah satu tempat yang wajib dikunjungi bagi pecinta kuliner dan mereka yang mencari tempat santai untuk bersantap. Terletak di jantung kota Kediri, kafe ini menawarkan pengalaman yang memuaskan untuk para pelanggan dengan suasana yang nyaman dan hidangan lezat. Dari luar, Kovii Cafe menarik perhatian dengan desain eksteriornya yang modern dan minimalis. Tapi yang membuat kafe ini benar-benar menonjol adalah ketika Anda memasuki pintu dan merasakan kehangatan yang disajikan oleh staf yang ramah. Mereka selalu siap untuk melayani Anda dengan senyum, membuat Anda merasa di rumah. Kovii Cafe menawarkan berbagai hidangan yang memikat, mulai dari kopi hingga makanan penutup yang lezat. Bagi para pencinta kopi, Anda akan dimanjakan dengan berbagai pilihan kopi, mulai dari espresso hingga kopi spesial. Kopi mereka selalu segar dan disajikan dengan sempurna. Tak hanya kopi, menu makanan di Kovii Cafe juga patut dicoba. Mereka menawarkan hidangan lokal dan internasional, mulai dari nasi goreng hingga pasta. Saya sangat merekomendasikan mencicipi Nasi Goreng Special Kovii - rasanya sungguh enak dan menggugah selera. Tempat ini juga sangat cocok untuk berbagai acara, mulai dari pertemuan bisnis hingga berkumpul dengan teman-teman. Mereka menyediakan area indoor yang nyaman serta outdoor yang asri. Suasana kafe ini tenang dan cocok untuk berbicara atau bekerja. Jika Anda adalah penggemar makanan penutup, pastikan untuk mencicipi kue-kue lezat yang mereka tawarkan. Pilihan kue yang beragam akan memanjakan lidah Anda. Saya pribadi sangat suka dengan Red Velvet Cake mereka - lembut, manis, dan memanjakan selera. Kovii Cafe Kediri juga cocok untuk acara keluarga. Mereka memiliki menu anak-anak yang lucu dan tempat bermain untuk anak-anak. Ini membuat kafe ini menjadi pilihan yang baik bagi keluarga yang ingin bersantap bersama. Harga di Kovii Cafe Kediri sangat terjangkau, mengingat kualitas makanan dan minuman yang mereka tawarkan. Ini adalah tempat yang ideal untuk bersantai dan menikmati hidangan lezat tanpa harus merogoh kocek terlalu dalam. Singkatnya, Kovii Cafe adalah tempat yang sempurna untuk bersantap, berkumpul, atau sekadar menikmati secangkir kopi yang nikmat. Dengan pelayanan ramah dan makanan yang lezat, tidak heran jika kafe ini menjadi favorit di kota Kediri. Jadi, jika Anda berada di Kediri, jangan lewatkan kesempatan untuk mengunjungi Kovii Cafe.
review_translated_text: Kovii Cafe, Kediri: Relaxing and Delicious Place to Dine Kovii Cafe in Kediri is a must-visit place for culinary lovers and those looking for a relaxing place to dine. Located in the heart of Kediri, this cafe offers a satisfying experience for customers with a comfortable atmosphere and delicious dishes. From the outside, Kovii Cafe attracts attention with its modern and minimalist exterior design. But what makes this cafe really stand out is when you enter the door and feel the warmth served by the friendly staff. They are always ready to serve you with a smile, making you feel at home. Kovii Cafe offers a variety of enticing dishes, from coffee to delicious desserts. For coffee lovers, you will be spoiled for choice with various coffee choices, from espresso to specialty coffee. Their coffee is always fresh and served perfectly. Not only coffee, the food menu at Kovii Cafe is also worth trying. They offer local and international dishes, from fried rice to pasta. I highly recommend tasting the Kovii Special Fried Rice - its really delicious and mouth-watering. This place is also very suitable for various events, from business meetings to gatherings with friends. They provide comfortable indoor and beautiful outdoor areas. The atmosphere of this cafe is calm and suitable for talking or working. If you are a fan of desserts, be sure to try the delicious cakes they offer. A wide selection of cakes will pamper your taste buds. I personally really like their Red Velvet Cake - soft, sweet and a treat to the taste buds. Kovii Cafe Kediri is also suitable for family events. They have a cute childrens menu and a play area for the kids. This makes this cafe a good choice for families who want to dine together. The prices at Kovii Cafe Kediri are very affordable, considering the quality of the food and drinks they offer. This is the ideal place to relax and enjoy a delicious meal without having to dig deep into your pockets. In short, Kovii Cafe is the perfect place to dine, gather or simply enjoy a delicious cup of coffee. With friendly service and delicious food, its no surprise that this cafe is a favorite in the city of Kediri. So, if you are in Kediri, dont miss the opportunity to visit Kovii Cafe.

review_text: Gak ada masalah sm menunya, cm yg membuat sy kecewa adl ketika sy membeli gelato, sy hanya memesan 3 cup. Dan setelah sy membayar dan masuk mobil, suami sy double check, trnyata yg di input 4cup. Akhirnya sy turun lagi untuk menanyakan. Ketika bertemu dengan mbak2 kasir yg sama, sy bertanya  mbak ini knp ada 4 cup ya? Ohh iya, yg 15rb sy refund yaa Ada yg janggal nggak sih? Seperti sudah tau kalo dilebihkan 1 cup, pdhl sy cuma blg 4 cup dan tidak menjelaskan lebihan cup nya berapa. Dan setelah itu di lanjut lagi  itu tadi teman sy yg bilang kalo ada 4 scoop . Dengan sangat santai nya dan tanpa merasa bersalah. Lgsg sy blg, silahkan mbak lihat di meja tempat sy tadi, ada brpa cup disana. (Disitu sudah mulai kesel dan pengen ngomel rasanya. Dan bayangkan kalo ada 1 item yg dilebihkan di 10 bill). Pdhl setelah sy memesan gelato, sy dengar sendiri temannya hanya menyebutkan 3 jenis gelato yg sy pesan. Santai sekali ngomongnya seakan sudah terbiasa dengan hal tsb. Sampai sy menerima uang refund pun dia tidak ada basa basi  Say sorry . Yg kedua, disana tadi tidak menyediakan cashless. Pdhl skrg udah sangat jarang sekali sy temukan pembayaran cash. Sangat tidak praktis menurut sy. Atau hanya trik dari mbak2 kasirnya? Sy tidak tau. Yg datang ke resto ini, tolong Double Check lagi pesanan kalian, biar hal seperti ini tidak terjadi lagi. Kalopun ada lgsg aja laporin ke atasannya.
review_translated_text: There was no problem with the menu, but what disappointed me was that when I bought gelato, I only ordered 3 cups. And after I paid and got into the car, my husband double checked, it turned out that the input was 4 cups. Finally I went down again to ask. When I met the same cashier, I asked, Miss, why do you have 4 cups? Oh yeah, Ill refund the 15 thousand Is there something odd? Its as if you already know that its 1 cup extra, even though I only said 4 cups and didnt explain how many cups it was. And after that it was continued that was my friend who said there were 4 scoops. Very relaxed and without feeling guilty. Immediately I said, please look at the table where I was, there are several cups there. (I was starting to get annoyed and wanted to grumble. And imagine if there was 1 item that was extra on 10 bills). Even after I ordered gelato, I heard my friend only mention 3 types of gelato that I ordered. He spoke so casually as if he was used to it. Until I received the refund, he didnt even say Say sorry. Second, there is no cashless service there. Even now, it is very rare for me to find cash payments. Very impractical in my opinion. Or is it just a trick from the cashiers? I dont know. Those who come to this restaurant, please double check your order again, so that something like this doesnt happen again. Even if there is, just report it to your superiors.

review_text: Without exaggeration, the single best meal weve had in all of Indonesia so far! This place is incredible. The atmosphere is a young, merry crowd of individuals who will sing along to great songs on the speakers or just play cards and chat with their friends, all in the late night. The seemingly quiet area is woken up by this place once you turn up and you can tell why. The staff were absolutely lovely too! Super friendly and tried incredibly hard to communicate with me and my wife in English. We ordered the Mie Bangla and a chicken and rice recipe but the Mie Bangla stole the show. Truly an outstanding dish that blew us away The lychee tea was also a massive hit and we loved it! I will say one thing that is synonymous across local cafes and restaurants around Java; there are not enough descriptions of each menu item and there are also no photos. To achieve five stars from me, there needs to be at least a menu with photos of each item plus descriptions, with an added bonus of uploading this to their Google maps too, it would have made our journey so much easier. That said, I loved this place so I commend the team for having such a great set up.

Karena cheesenya sendiri sudah cukup manis bagi saya yang tidak suka manis ini bikin eneg. Saya pikir beefnya dapat bacon atau slice beef karena harganya cukup mahal tapi malah dapat ham. Tapi ketika teman saya memesan indonesia cuisenenya mereka bilang cukup enak, sambalnya juga enak. Tahunya juara bau bawang putih dan rempah2nya bikin nambah nafsu makan. review_translated_text: The drink is delicious, the price is quite cheap, the taste of the coffee is also great. Its just that the food is quite expensive and I ordered Egg with smokey beef, it tasted like it made me feel bad, I needed pepper so that the fishy smell of the egg disappeared and there wasnt enough salt. Because the cheese itself is sweet enough for me, who doesnt like sweets, this makes me nervous. I thought the beef would get bacon or sliced beef because the price was quite expensive but instead I got ham. But when my friends ordered the Indonesian cuisine they said it was quite delicious, the chili sauce was also delicious. Its known that the smell of garlic and spices increases your appetite. The pastries are also delicious at this cafe. In terms of space, its spacious, aesthetic and shady so its not hot during the day

review_translated_text: When I first stopped by, I was a little annoyed because on the GPS it said it opened at 11.00, but when I got there, the seller said that it only opened at 12.00. its okay. the annoyance disappeared because the place was exactly as I thought it would be; beautiful, classic, comfortable. just a little hot at the top. but the food and drinks are affordable. Every corner is decorated with vintage items, there are lots of books to read, and there is also a large space for doing homework and just relaxing. I wanted to say this to Cafe Gresiknesia; If its close to home, Ill definitely stop by often! Haha.

review_text: Lunacia Cafe, Kediri: Kopi dan Kenyamanan dalam Satu Tempat Lunacia Cafe di Kediri adalah tempat yang patut dicoba bagi pecinta kopi dan pencari suasana santai. Terletak di jantung kota Kediri, kafe ini menawarkan pengalaman unik dengan kopi yang lezat dan suasana yang nyaman. Saat pertama kali masuk ke Lunacia Cafe, Anda akan langsung terpesona oleh dekorasi yang indah dan atmosfer yang hangat. Kafe ini dirancang dengan penuh perhatian terhadap detail, menciptakan suasana yang sempurna untuk bersantai atau berkumpul dengan teman-teman. Menu kopi di Lunacia Cafe sangat beragam. Mereka menawarkan berbagai jenis kopi, mulai dari espresso yang kuat hingga kopi susu yang lembut. Pilihan kopi mereka selalu segar dan disajikan dengan apik. Barista di sini benar-benar ahli dalam seni kopi. Selain kopi, Lunacia Cafe juga menawarkan berbagai minuman non-kopi seperti teh dan minuman segar. Jadi, meskipun Anda bukan penggemar kopi, Anda masih bisa menikmati waktu yang menyenangkan di sini. Menu makanan di Lunacia Cafe juga patut dicoba. Mereka menyajikan hidangan lokal dan internasional. Sarapan pagi dengan croissant yang lembut dan telur dadar adalah salah satu favorit saya. Atau Anda bisa mencoba hidangan berat seperti pasta atau burger yang lezat. Tempat ini juga sangat cocok untuk bekerja atau bersantai. Mereka menyediakan Wi-Fi yang cepat dan colokan listrik, sehingga Anda bisa membawa laptop dan bekerja dengan nyaman. Musik latar yang lembut dan suasana yang tenang membuatnya menjadi tempat yang ideal untuk berkonsentrasi. Lunacia Cafe juga sering mengadakan acara-acara tematik seperti pertunjukan musik langsung atau pameran seni. Jadi, pastikan untuk memeriksa jadwal acara mereka jika Anda ingin merasakan pengalaman yang lebih unik. Karyawan di Lunacia Cafe selalu siap untuk melayani Anda dengan ramah dan senyum. Mereka tahu betul cara membuat pengunjung merasa dihargai. Pelayanan yang baik selalu menjadi nilai tambah. Harga di Lunacia Cafe juga terjangkau, mengingat kualitas kopi dan makanan yang mereka tawarkan. Ini adalah tempat yang sempurna untuk menghabiskan waktu bersama teman-teman atau untuk pertemuan bisnis yang santai. Singkatnya, Lunacia Cafe adalah tempat yang wajib dikunjungi jika Anda berada di Kediri. Dengan suasana yang nyaman, kopi yang lezat, dan pilihan makanan yang menggugah selera, ini adalah tempat yang sempurna untuk bersantai dan menikmati hidangan lezat. Jadi, jangan ragu untuk menjadwalkan kunjungan Anda ke Lunacia Cafe dan nikmati pengalaman yang tak terlupakan.
review_translated_text: Lunacia Cafe, Kediri: Coffee and Comfort in One Place Lunacia Cafe in Kediri is a place worth trying for coffee lovers and those looking for a relaxed atmosphere. Located in the heart of Kediri, this cafe offers a unique experience with delicious coffee and a comfortable atmosphere. When you first enter Lunacia Cafe, you will immediately be enchanted by the beautiful decoration and warm atmosphere. The cafe is designed with attention to detail, creating the perfect atmosphere for relaxing or hanging out with friends. The coffee menu at Lunacia Cafe is very diverse. They offer a variety of coffees, from strong espresso to smooth milk coffee. Their coffee selection is always fresh and nicely presented. The baristas here are truly masters of the art of coffee. Apart from coffee, Lunacia Cafe also offers various non-coffee drinks such as tea and fresh drinks. So, even if youre not a coffee fan, you can still have a great time here. The food menu at Lunacia Cafe is also worth trying. They serve local and international dishes. Breakfast with soft croissants and omelettes is one of my favorites. Or you can try a heavy meal like pasta or a delicious burger. This place is also very suitable for working or relaxing. They provide fast Wi-Fi and power outlets, so you can bring your laptop and work comfortably. Soft background music and a calm atmosphere make it an ideal place to concentrate. Lunacia Cafe also often holds thematic events such as live music performances or art exhibitions. So, be sure to check out their event schedule if you want a more unique experience. Employees at Lunacia Cafe are always ready to serve you with kindness and a smile. They really know how to make visitors feel appreciated. Good service is always an added value. The prices at Lunacia Cafe are also affordable, considering the quality of the coffee and food they offer. This is the perfect place to spend time with friends or for a casual business meeting. In short, Lunacia Cafe is a must-visit place if you are in Kediri. With a cozy atmosphere, delicious coffee and mouth-watering food options, its the perfect place to relax and enjoy a delicious meal. So, dont hesitate to schedule your visit to Lunacia Cafe and enjoy an unforgettable experience.

review_text: Baru pertama kali coba, pesan beberapa menu (mie ghibah lv 1, mie ghibah lv 0, red Velvet, taro) Red Velvet enak rasanya, mirip mirip kayak minuman pop ice gitu. Minuman rasa taro enak, tapi kemanisan banget. Mie ghibah level 0 ngga beda jauh sama mie yg lain (kayak mie Tek Tek gitu sih). Kalau yang level 1 rasanya lebih beda dan pedes banget. Kata pegawainya level 1 itu cabainya 5. Kalau ngga kuat pedes, lebih baik level 0 aja, atau kalo bisa request yaa cabainya dikurangin aja, karena level 1 pedes banget banget. Dalam 1 piring mie, terdiri dari mie, tomat, kubis gitu deh (lupa namanya), timun, kerupuk pangsit 2, daging slice 2 tapi ga kerasa daging banget, dan taburan putih putih, kayaknya sih bukan ayam suwir gitu, rasanya persis sama kerupuk udang yg dihalusin atau kayak koya soto. Suasana: tenang, ada musik, toilet, tempat parkir berbayar, namun di lantai 2 kursi pinggir dekat jendela dan jalan itu kelihatan atapnya kotor ada daun-daun kering banyak. Rasa: lumayan
review_translated_text: Just trying it for the first time, order several menus (mi Ghibah lv 1, noodle ghibah lv 0, red Velvet, taro) Red Velvet tastes delicious, similar to an ice pop drink. The taro flavored drink is delicious, but very sweet. Ghibah level 0 noodles are not much different from other noodles (like Tek Tek noodles). If you have level 1, the taste is different and really spicy. The employee said that level 1 chili has 5. If its not very spicy, its better to just level 0, or if you can request it, just reduce the chili, because level 1 is very spicy. In 1 plate of noodles, consisting of noodles, tomatoes, cabbage like that (forgot the name), cucumber, 2 wonton crackers, 2 slices of meat but it doesnt really taste like meat, and white sprinkles, I dont think its shredded chicken, it tastes exactly the same as crackers crushed shrimp or something like koya soto. Atmosphere: calm, there is music, toilets, paid parking, but on the 2nd floor the edge seats near the window and the road look like the roof is dirty and there are lots of dry leaves. Taste: not bad

review_text: Ke sini pesen minuman namanya Chocoa, dan yang dateng susu, coklat asli yang rasanya pahit, dan krimer yang rasanya manis-manis enak yang gak begitu manis. Jadi saya happy banget. Soalnya biasanya kalo pesen minuman susu coklat di tempat lain dikasihnya kadang minuman serbuk yang diseduh pake air. Terus juga pesen nasi goreng solaria. Rasa nasi gorengnya lumayan, sayang sekali gak ada telur ceplok dan kerupuknya, padahal itu sangat esensial buat nasi goreng. Terus bakarannya juga enak, bumbunya meresap. Saran dicek lagi kondisi telurnya. Suasana tempatnya juga cukup nyaman karena tidak begitu berisik meski di pinggir jalan. Harga makanannya sesuai lah dengan apa yang di dapat.
review_translated_text: Here, I ordered a drink called Chocoa, and what came was milk, real chocolate which tasted bitter, and creamer which tasted deliciously sweet which wasnt too sweet. So Im really happy. The problem is that usually when you order a chocolate milk drink at another place they sometimes give you a powdered drink brewed using water. Then also order Solaria fried rice. The taste of the fried rice is not bad, its a shame it doesnt have fried eggs and crackers, even though those are very essential for fried rice. Then the grill is also delicious, the spices are absorbed. Advice to check the condition of the eggs again. The atmosphere of the place is also quite comfortable because it is not too noisy even though it is on the side of the road. The price of the food is in accordance with what you get.

review_text: Favorite place to hang out with my kids and wife Until all the baristas became my childrens best friends hahaha

Ketemu comfort zone di BWI Lagi muter cari2 tempat ngopi enak maksudnya biar bisa sekalian kerja laptop an, memang ada beberapa tempat yg cocok ya tapi sayangnya buat saya terlalu penuh dan sesak.. akhirnya cari2 lagi dan ketemu dengan Sukaria ini.. tempatnya nyaman, kids friendly, makanannya juga enak,ada beberapa pilihan makanan, hampir semua saya coba dan rasanya enak dan harganya juga ok. Saya coba kopi dan STMJnya enak sekaliii (lain dari yg lain) saya tanya2 ternyata memang belajar khusus sama ahlinya.. Hebatt!!! Saya pikir menarik sih ini.. Datang kesini dengan keluarga atau teman2... ada live music setiap hari Rabu dan Sabtu .. I highly recommend their STMJ, Kopi Sukaria and Cwimie (my ultimate favourite) was excellent.. Nyenengin banget disana.. staff nya ramah2 dan ngasi info ke saya tempat2 menarik di BWI untuk dikunjungi.. Sukses terus buat Sukaria.. Sampai jumpa di lain kesempatan bolo2!! Saya pasti balik lagi. Bali, 17 Maret 2024

review_translated_text: Find the comfort zone at BWI I was wandering around looking for a good place to drink coffee so I could work on my laptop at the same time. There were indeed several places that were suitable, but unfortunately for me it was too full and cramped... finally I looked around again and found this Sukaria... the place is comfortable, kids friendly, the food is also delicious , there are several food choices, I tried almost all of them and they taste delicious and the prices are also ok. I tried the coffee and the STMJ was really delicious (different from the others). I asked around and it turned out that I had studied specifically with an expert... Great!!! I think this is interesting... Come here with family or friends... there is live music every Wednesday and Saturday.. I highly recommend their STMJ, Kopi Sukaria and Cwimie (my ultimate favorite) was excellent.. It was really fun there.. the staff were friendly and gave me information about interesting places in BWI to visit.. Continued success for Sukaria.. See you next time guys!! Ill definitely come back again. Bali, March 17 2024

My thoughts about Kedai Dimar: == Location == Berlokasi strategis tepat di jalan Ahmad Dahlan, Mojoroto serta tepat bersebelahan dengan kampus UNP Kediri. Akan mudah untuk ditemui karena berada di jalan utama serta tepat berseberangan dengan Indomaret. Selain itu, penanda logo tempat yang menempel di kaca depan kurang terlihat dan cenderung terkesan gelap karena sebagian tertutup dengan dedaunan. == Visual == Seluruh ruangan didesain dengan konsep serius dan vintage namun segar, dibentuk dari kombinasi warna hitam, abu-abu dan coklat. Banyaknya dedaunan yang menghiasi serta nyempil inilah terasa menyegarkan. Ruangan juga disinari oleh lampu kekuningan pada hampir setiap mejanya yang menambah kesan warm. == Audio == Dalam sisi audio, disisipi playlist yang hits lintas dekade dengan kuantitas yang nyaman didengarkan pada setiap ruangannya. Ruangan didesain tertutup ini dilengkapi AC menjadikan distorsi suara jalanan yang tereduksi, walaupun kurang mereduksi suara dari seringnya kendaraan muatan berat. == Menu == Menu yang disediakan sangat bervariatif, dari snack hingga main course yg disajikan dengan apik dengan sajian yang tepat. == Drink == Minuman yang tersedia dari varian non-kopi hingga kopi yang disajikan dengan apik. == Features == Disediakan toilet/WC dengan pas nan bersih. Ketersediaan set meja-kursi juga pas, adapun beberapa set meja-sofa walau terciprat air kebocoran apabila hujan yang sangat deras mengguyur. Ruangan juga didekorasi ornamen-ornamen yang menunjukkan ciri vintage-nya. Mayoritas tersedia slot listrik serta akses wi-fi. Untuk parkir hanya pada di depan ruko, namun kemungkinan akan kesusahan parkir untuk kendaraan beroda empat. Dalam beberapa waktu, disuguhkan live music. * Jadi, Kedai Dimar ini sangatlah tepat untuk pelanggan yang menginginkan suasana chill dan nyaman, baik bersama sosialnya hingga individualnya, keluarga hingga pekerjaannya disandingkan dengan hidangan yang dipesan. Sekian. Thanks.
response_from_owner_text: Terima kasih
review_translated_text: My thoughts about Kedai Dimar: ==Location== Strategically located right on Jalan Ahmad Dahlan, Mojoroto and right next to the UNP Kediri campus. It will be easy to find because it is on the main road and right opposite Indomaret. Apart from that, the logo marker attached to the windshield is less visible and tends to appear dark because it is partially covered by leaves. ==Visuals== The entire room is designed with a serious and vintage but fresh concept, formed from a combination of black, gray and brown. The abundance of foliage that decorates and looks refreshing. The room is also illuminated by yellowish lights on almost every table which adds a warm impression. ==Audio== On the audio side, a playlist of hits across decades is included in a quantity that is comfortable to listen to in any room. This closed designed room is equipped with air conditioning so that street sound distortion is reduced, although it does not reduce the sound from frequent heavy vehicles. ==Menu== The menu provided is very varied, from snacks to main courses which are presented nicely with the right dishes. ==Drink== The drinks available range from non-coffee to coffee variants which are served nicely. == Features == Proper and clean toilets/WCs are provided. The availability of table-chair sets is also good, while several table-sofa sets are splashed with water leaks when it rains very heavily. The room is also decorated with ornaments that show its vintage characteristics. The majority have electricity slots and wi-fi access. Parking is only in front of the shophouse, but it may be difficult to park four-wheeled vehicles. At some times, live music is presented. * So, Kedai Dimar is very suitable for customers who want a chill and comfortable atmosphere, both social and individual, family and work combined with the dishes ordered. Thats all. Thanks.
response_from_owner_translated_text: Thank you

response_from_owner_text: Halo, terima kasih kak frida florentina atas review bintang 1 nya. Untuk kronologinya tadi kakak datang pada saat buka puasa yang mana hampir semua pelanggan kami melakukan reservasi. Sedangkan kakak tidak ada reservasi. Kemudian pegawai kami menginfo bahwa sedang ramai. Yang mana kaka masuk dan melihat kondisinya, dan kami menyarankan menu yang cepat prosesnya. Seperti nasi telur chungking dan nasi telur tomat dll. Tapi kakak tetap menolak dan memesan sapo tofu, ayam mentega, laksa. Sedangkan 2 meja lain di dalam menunggu lebih lama dari kaka dan sabar. Bahkan pegawai kami meminta maaf 3 kali dan kaka tetap ngomel2. Kemudian mengeluhkan tidak ada ikan, maaf kak kalo resto kami ga jual ikan bakar atau ikan cupang    Tapi makanan semua yang kaka pesan habis dan bahkan di take away. Kalo harga mahal maafkan kami kak. Harga bahan emang lagi mahal  . Dan kebetulan kami memang mau tutup libur lebaran jadi kaka tenang saja tidak usah menyuruh kami tutup. Kami juga sudah melihat review kaka di resto lain kok. Kami meminta maaf dan berjanji akan memperbaiki terus pelayanan kami. Sehat selalu kakak cantik
review_translated_text: The service took a really long time, it didnt finish for an hour, there was no fish in the dish, only vegetables, the price was quite expensive, please respect the buyers, dont be slow to cook, if you cant cook quickly its better to just close it, hahahaha
response_from_owner_translated_text: Hello, thank you Sis Frida Florentina for your 1 star review. For the chronology, you came at the time of breaking the fast, where almost all of our customers made reservations. Meanwhile, my sister didnt have a reservation. Then our employee informed us that it was busy. Which means you come in and see the conditions, and we suggest a menu that is a fast process. Such as Chungking egg rice and tomato egg rice etc. But my brother still refused and ordered sapo tofu, butter chicken, laksa. Meanwhile, 2 other tables inside waited longer than Kaka and were patient. Even our employees apologized 3 times and Kaka still grumbled. Then complained that there was no fish, sorry sis if our restaurant doesnt sell grilled fish or betta fish    But all the food you ordered was gone and they were even taken away. If the price is expensive, were sorry. The price of materials is really expensive  . And coincidentally, we really want to close for the Eid holiday, so dont worry, you dont need to tell us to close. Weve also seen Kakas reviews at other restaurants. We apologize and promise to continue to improve our services. Always healthy, beautiful sister

Overall 4/5

review_text: Nemu begitu aja pas naik mobil dan emang pengin istirahat: duduk, minum, ngobrol. Kami berempat datang dari luar kota, jadi emang ga tahu tempat main di kota Banyuwangi. Kami terpikat buat mampir karena desain depannya seru, lucu. Pas masuk, makin lucu; warna tempatnya, dekorasinya, desainnya thoughtful. Bir dan dimsum nyambung, jadi kami senang aja duduk di sini lama-lama. Ada layar besar di outdoornya, yang mungkin buat nonton bareng kalo ada acara, yang pas kami datang (kami kebetulan datang pas lagi sepi pengunjung), langsung diputarkan video tentang alam tanpa suara. Musik yang diputar volumenya pas, sehingga kami masih bisa ngobrol dengan nyaman tanpa teriak-teriak. Enak ini, aku suka. Menurutku harganya pas dengan rasa makan, suasana, kenyamanan. Jarang sekali ada tempat nongkrong yang se-thoughtful ini. Namun karena capek tapi senang sama tempatnya, aku ga foto makanan dan ruangannya. Foto2 sendiri aja huehehe

review_translated_text: Just met when I was in the car and really wanted to rest: sit, drink, chat. The four of us came from outside the city, so we didnt know where to play in Banyuwangi city. We were tempted to stop by because the front design was fun and cute. When you enter, it gets even funnier; the color of the place, the decoration, the thoughtful design. Beer and dimsum go hand in hand, so were just happy to sit here for a long time. There is a large screen outside, which is possible for watching together if there is an event, when we came (we happened to come when there were no visitors), a video about nature was immediately played without sound. The volume of the music being played was just right, so we could still chat comfortably without shouting. This is delicious, I like it. In my opinion, the price is right for the taste, atmosphere, comfort. Its rare to find a place to hang out as thoughtful as this. However, because I was tired but happy with the place, I didnt take photos of the food and the room. Just take your own photos hehehe

Sampang, Jawa Timur ini memang selalu menjadi destinasi liburan favorit karena banyak hal yang bisa dieksplor dan selalu ada saja yang baru. Kreativitas warga sampang, terutama di bidang kuliner, tak ada habisnya. Menjamurnya kafe-kafe yang nyaman dan interior yang unik membuat kita ingin mencoba semuanya. Sampang is a city full of attractions and always has something to make anyone miss. Sampang, East Java has always been a favorite holiday destination because there are lots of things to explore and there is always something new. The creativity of Sampang residents, especially in the culinary field, is endless. The proliferation of comfortable cafes and unique interiors makes us want to try everything. place_name: Tuk Tuk Tea (The Real Thai Tea)
review_text: Sumpah pengalaman terburuk saat membeli tuk tuk tea, di cabang Indomaret Batangan/perbatasan situbondo mau masuk hutan baluran, pelayanan sangat TIDAK RAMAH bukan hanya ke saya tp ke bbrp orng ternyata jg sama, menggebrok gebrok saat melayani, ketus saat ditanyai, tidak senyum sama sekali, bahkah saat sy mengucapkan terimakasih tidak dijawab. Kalo hanya sekali saya memaklumi mungkin capek tapi ini setiap saya beli ksn pelayanan sama bahkan sy pernah adu mulut, saya tanya bbrp varian dia tdk menjawab karena rasa jengkel uang saya lempar dan dia bilang TIDAK SOPAN padahal dia pelayanan sangat tidak etis. mulai sekarang saya dan keluarga saya tidak akan membeli tuk tuk tea walaupun itu minuman kesukaan saya, sudah terlanjur males lapor ke admin hanya iya iya saja. TERIMAKASIH
review_translated_text: I swear, the worst experience was when buying tuk tuk tea, at the Indomaret Batangan branch/Situbondo border, about to enter the Baluran forest, the service was very UNFRIENDLY, not only to me but to several people, it turned out to be the same, banging when serving, curt when asked, didnt smile at all , even when I said thank you there was no answer. If its just once, I understand that maybe Im tired, but this is every time I buy from the same service, I even had an argument, I asked several variants, he didnt answer because I was annoyed, I threw the money and he said NOT POOL even though his service was very unethical. From now on, my family and I will not buy tuk tuk tea even though its my favorite drink, Im too lazy to report to admin just yes, yes. THANK YOU

review_text: Salah satu pilihan cafe terbaik di Banyuwangi, lokasinya berada di pusat kota. dekat dengan stasiun karangasem, dekat dengan homestay. Jika anda turis mancanegara dan ingin menikmati bir dingin di tengah panas nya cuaca tropis, Moxie coffee mungkin salah satu pilihan terbaik, jika bukan satu satunya cafe yg legal menjual bir dingin di Banyuwangi. Walaupun lokasinya berada dalam satu kompleks area Aston Hotel, akan tetapi, Moxie coffee terbuka bagi tamu umum, bukan hanya yang menginap di Aston Hotel. menu makanan yg bisa saya rekomendasi kan nachos dan pizza nya yang enak.
review_translated_text: One of the best cafe choices in Banyuwangi, located in the city center. close to Karangasem station, close to homestay. If you are a foreign tourist and want to enjoy cold beer in the hot tropical weather, Moxie Coffee is probably one of the best choices, if not the only cafe that legally sells cold beer in Banyuwangi. Even though it is located in the Aston Hotel area complex, Moxie Coffee is open to general guests, not just those staying at the Aston Hotel. The food menu that I can recommend is the delicious nachos and pizza.

Mulai dari bentuknya, bukaan kaca yang banyak, jenis kursi yang digunakan juga warna yang dipadukan sangat cocok untuk tempat bersantai dari jenuhnya bekerja. Mulai masuk ke dalam cafenya, ternyata ada ACnya yang membuat suasana didalam cafe lebih nyaman lagi buat nongkrong. Tempatnya juga bersih dan terawat. ---Pelayanan--- Pelayanannya sangat bagus, kasirnya ramah, waiternya juga ramah. ---Menu--- Menu yang ditawarkan cukup beragam, mulai dari kopi kopian (namanya juga cafe :)), mojito dan juga milkbase. Makanannya juga cukup beragam mulai dari makanan berat hingga cemilan. Harganya juga beragam mulai dari 7 ribu kalo ga salah hingga 20ribuan. ---Rasa--- Rasanya yang disajikan ga mengecewakan. Meskipun harganya terbilang murah, rasanya tidak murahan. Mulai dari minumannya hingga makanannya ga ada yang mengecewakan. ---Fasilitas--- Fasilitas yang disediakan juga cukup oke. Seperti yang dijelaskan diatas, tersedia Air Conditioner(AC), toilet yabg mewah, Wi-Fi tentunya, serta stop kontak yang tersedia didekat gedung di titik tertentu. Juga tersedia proyektor sehingga anda dapat melaksanakan meeting di cafe ini. Itu saja dari saya, Overall Cafe ini worth it banget buat dikunjungi. ~Mari saling berbagi~ .
review_translated_text: ---Place--- Just entering, the parking lot is large enough for many motorbikes and several cars because it is in the same place as the car wash. At first glance from the outside, the cafe looks really cozy from the outside. Starting from the shape, the many glass openings, the type of chairs used and the colors combined, it is very suitable for a place to relax from the boredom of work. Starting to enter the cafe, it turns out there is air conditioning which makes the atmosphere in the cafe even more comfortable for hanging out. The place is also clean and well maintained. ---Service--- The service was very good, the cashier was friendly, the waiter was also friendly. ---Menu--- The menu offered is quite varied, starting from coffee coffee (also called a cafe :)), mojito and also milkbase. The food is also quite varied, from heavy meals to snacks. Prices also vary from 7 thousand if Im not mistaken to 20 thousand. ---Flavor--- The taste served does not disappoint. Even though the price is relatively cheap, it doesnt taste cheap. From the drinks to the food, nothing disappoints. ---Facility--- The facilities provided are also quite good. As explained above, there is air conditioning (AC), luxurious toilets, Wi-Fi of course, and power sockets available near the building at certain points. There is also a projector available so you can hold meetings at this cafe. Thats all from me, Overall this Cafe is really worth visiting. ~Lets share with each other~ .

review_text: lokasi cafe di GKB. salah satu cafe dengan lampu terang dan membuat nuansa lebih cerah, ornamen cafe jadi lebih terlihat. spot favorit ada di lantai 2 dengan nuansa cozy, ac terasa dingin, ada spot live musiccc juga. untuk harga makanan dan minuman standard cafe juga porsi makanan yang disediakan cukup sesuai dengan harga. pelayanan cukup ramah, metode pembayaran bisa tunai maupun qris. tapi sayang sekali, saat kesini selesai payment 19.25, makanan datang sekitar 19.54 dan minuman baru datang di 20.15. mungkin karena situasi agak ramai dan staff jaga hanya 2 orang. Parking: parkir motor bisa di depan cafe dan berbayar 2ribu. untuk parkir mobil yang agak sulit ditemukan. Kid-friendliness: tersedia baby chair
review_translated_text: cafe location in GKB. one of the cafes with bright lights makes the atmosphere brighter, the cafe ornaments become more visible. Favorite spot is on the 2nd floor with a cozy feel, the AC feels cold, there is a live music spot too. For standard cafe food and drink prices, the portions of food provided are quite in line with the price. The service is quite friendly, payment methods can be cash or qris. but unfortunately, when I finished paying here at 19.25, the food arrived around 19.54 and the drinks only arrived at 20.15. maybe because the situation was a bit crowded and there were only 2 staff on duty. Parking: You can park your motorbike in front of the cafe and pay 2 thousand. for car parking which is a bit difficult to find. Kid-friendliness: baby chair available

review_text: Sabtu, 10 Februari 2024 18.00 WIB Overall bintang 4/5 Makanan & Minuman : 4,5/5 - Harga relatif standar untuk cafe 4/5. - Pesan matcha latte juga tergolong cukup enak 4/5 (rasa matchanya kerasa, bahkan setelah es batu mencair) ga enek, ini type matcha yg light. - Recommended buat kalian yg suka kopi tp bukan strong, bisa pesen hazelnut latte. 10/5 Enak banget - Untuk mix samplernya rasanya cukup enak, porsi cukup hanya untuk 2 orang. 4/5 - Untuk Ayam sambal matahnya, ayamnya enak, matangnya pas, nasinya juga ga kering, telurnya oke. Sambalnya juga fresh. 4,5/5 Waktu tunggu makanan & minuman sekitar 5-15 menit cukup cepat dibandingkan cafe lain. 4,5/5 Metode pembayaran : 5/5 - Bisa pake qris dan menerima qris dari Dana, mbanking, dll. Sangat bagus, apalagi untuk org yg jarang bawa uang cash hehe Parkir : 4/5 - Ada biaya parkir 2000 untuk motor, jd siapkan uang kecil ya. Walaupun ukuran parkirnya kecil tp penataan oke. Suasana cafe : 5/5 - Suasana ramai atau sepi tetap nyaman, kebetulan saya dtg wkt sepi lalu ga lama ramai. - Ada mainan yg bisa digunakan untuk anak & org dewasa. - Banyak spot menarik untuk foto, yg tentunya aesthetic ya. - Ini poin plus ada baby chairnya, ga banyak cafe ngasih ini, but good job. Layanan : 3,5/5 - Untuk kasir atau barista, awalnya saya biasa saja krn memang mereka ramah, sopan, dan cukup tanggap dgn pertanyaan saya. - Saya meminta tambahan saus pun tetap dilayani dgn baik. Note Kekurangan : - Hanya sedikit kekurangan tp mohon diperbaiki ya, saya meminta sambal matah pesanan saya dipisah, dan tentu diiyakan oleh kasir, tp ntah kenapa saat disajikan pada akhirnya sambalnya digabung. Apakah miskom dari bagian masak atau kasirnya, saya kurang tahu. Tp mohon diperbaiki lagi ya. Mungkin ini hal sepele, tp bisa jadi krusial bagi sebagian org, karna setiap org punya alasan tersendiri. Semoga dapat menjadi masukan untuk kedepannya. Kalau ditanya mau balik lagi? Mungkin saya akan kembali lagi, terima kasih. Semoga sukses unice :) Kid-friendliness: Cocok untuk bersantai dgn bawa anak, krn ada baby chair dan mainan untuk anak anak.

review_translated_text: Saturday, February 10 2024 18.00 WIB Overall 4/5 stars Food & Drink : 4.5/5 - Prices are relatively standard for cafes 4/5. - The matcha latte order is also quite delicious 4/5 (the matcha taste is strong, even after the ice cubes melt) not bad, this is a light type of matcha. - Recommended for those of you who like coffee but not strong, you can order the hazelnut latte. 10/5 Very tasty - The mix sampler tastes quite good, the portion is only enough for 2 people. 4/5 - For the sambal matah chicken, the chicken is delicious, cooked just right, the rice isnt dry, the eggs are okay. The chili sauce is also fresh. 4.5/5 The waiting time for food & drinks is around 5-15 minutes, which is quite fast compared to other cafes. 4.5/5 Payment method : 5/5 - Can use qris and receive qris from Dana, mbanking, etc. Very good, especially for people who rarely carry cash hehe Parking : 4/5 - There is a parking fee of 2000 for motorbikes, so prepare a small amount of money. Even though the parking area is small, the layout is okay. Cafe atmosphere: 5/5 - The atmosphere is still comfortable whether its busy or quiet, I happened to come when it was quiet and then it wasnt busy for long. - There are toys that can be used for children & adults. - Lots of interesting spots for photos, which are of course aesthetic. - This is a plus point because there is a baby chair, not many cafes provide this, but good job. Service : 3.5/5 - For cashiers or baristas, at first I was okay with it because they were friendly, polite and quite responsive to my questions. - I asked for extra sauce and it was still served well. Note Disadvantages: - Theres just a little flaw but please fix it, I asked for my order of sambal matah separately, and of course the cashier agreed, but for some reason when it was served, the chili sauce ended up being combined. Whether the miskom was from the cooking department or the cashier, I dont know. But please fix it again. Maybe this is a trivial thing, but it can be crucial for some people, because each person has their own reasons. Hopefully this can be input for the future. If asked, would you like to come back again? Maybe Ill come back again, thank you. Good luck unice :) Kid-friendliness: Suitable for relaxing with children, because there are baby chairs and toys for children.

review_text: Cangkrukan adalah restoran yang nyaman dan menyenangkan untuk menghabiskan waktu bersama teman atau keluarga. Suasana restorannya sangat santai dengan dekorasi yang unik dan menarik. Menu makanannya beragam dan lezat, terutama hidangan tradisional Indonesia seperti nasi goreng, mie goreng spageti Selain itu, mereka juga menyajikan minuman segar seperti es teh dan es jeruk yang sangat menyegarkan. Pelayanannya ramah dan cepat, membuat pengalaman makan di Cangkrukan menjadi menyenangkan. Harga makanan dan minumannya juga terjangkau. Jadi, jika Anda mencari tempat yang hangat dan enak untuk berkumpul, Cangkrukan adalah pilihan yang tepat!

review_translated_text: Cangkrukan is a comfortable and pleasant restaurant to spend time with friends or family. The atmosphere of the restaurant is very relaxed with unique and attractive decoration. The food menu is varied and delicious, especially traditional Indonesian dishes such as fried rice, fried noodles, spaghetti. Apart from that, they also serve fresh drinks such as iced tea and orange ice are very refreshing. The service is friendly and fast, making the experience of eating at Cangkrukan enjoyable. The prices of food and drinks are also affordable. So, if you are looking for a warm and nice place to gather, Cangkrukan is the right choice !
